```plantuml
@startuml spikecodes_stotra

actor User
participant Frontend as FE
participant "AWS Amplify" as Amplify
participant "Node.js/Express Backend" as BE
participant "AWS EC2" as EC2
participant MongoDB
participant "Yahoo Finance API" as YahooAPI
participant "Alpha Vantage API" as AlphaAPI

User -> FE : Access Frontend
FE -> Amplify : Deploy React App
FE -> BE : Request Stock Data
BE -> EC2 : Host Backend on EC2
BE -> MongoDB : Fetch User Data
BE -> YahooAPI : Fetch Real-time Stock Data
BE -> AlphaAPI : Fetch Historical Stock Data
BE -> FE : Return Stock Data
FE -> User : Display Data

User -> FE : Login/Signup
FE -> BE : Authenticate User
BE -> MongoDB : Verify User Credentials
BE -> FE : Return JWT Token
FE -> User : Provide Access

User -> FE : Update Watchlist
FE -> BE : Send Watchlist Update
BE -> MongoDB : Store Watchlist Data
BE -> FE : Confirm Update

@enduml
```